{"word":"G3708 - ὁράω - horáō - hor-ah'-o - Behold","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὁράω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>horáō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>hor-ah'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Behold"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - காண்பி, எச்சரிக்கையாயிரு, பார், காண், தரிசி"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to see to, look to"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> Properly to <i>stare</i> at (compare <a href=\"#/G3700 - ὀπτάνομαι - optánomai - op-tan'-om-ahee/3700\">G3700</a>), that is, (by implication) to <i>discern</i> clearly (physically or mentally); by extension to <i>attend</i> to; by Hebraism to <i>experience</i>; passively to <i>appear:</i> - behold, perceive, see, take heed."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2300 - θεάομαι - theáomai - theh-ah'-om-ahee/2300\">G2300</a>, <a href=\"#/G2334 - θεωρέω - theōréō - theh-o-reh'-o/2334\">G2334</a>, <a href=\"#/G2529 - καθοράω - kathoráō - kath-or-ah'-o/2529\">G2529</a>, <a href=\"#/G3705 - ὅραμα - hórama - hor'-am-ah/3705\">G3705</a>, <a href=\"#/G3706 - ὅρασις - hórasis - hor'-as-is/3706\">G3706</a>, <a href=\"#/G3707 - ὁρατός - horatós - hor-at-os'/3707\">G3707</a>, <a href=\"#/G3708 - ὁράω - horáō - hor-ah'-o/3708\">G3708</a>, <a href=\"#/G4308 - προοράω - prooráō - pro-or-ah'-o/4308\">G4308</a>, <a href=\"#/G517 - ἀόρατος - aóratos - ah-or'-at-os/517\">G517</a>"}]}